dcterms:description: A dataset containing audio samples of 1,006 instruments, each labeled with a unique pitch, timbre, and envelope. Each sample is a four-second monophonic 16kHz snippet, ranging over every pitch of a standard MIDI piano (21-108) as well as five different velocities. It was not seen during the training of the system.
dcterms:title: NSynth

dcterms:description: A dataset collected from professional musicians, used for training the model.
dcterms:title: Dataset collected from professional musicians
